cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY 

The paper proposes a Deep Neural Network model for thermal-inertial odometry, which involves computer vision, robotics, machine learning, and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and control (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and systems and control (cs.SY) as the secondary categories.
